Using jQuery Cycle plugin http://jquery.malsup.com/cycle/

View demo here: http://labs.mmikkel.no/jquery-responsive-cycle/demo.html

A basic jQuery Cycle plugin slideshow, implemented with responsive width handling.

This implementation works with the following markup:

<div class="container">
	<div class="cycle-slides">
		<div class="cycle-slide" />
		<div class="cycle-slide" />
		<div class="cycle-slide" />
	</div>
	<div class="cycle-pager"></div>
</div>

Usage:

<script type="text/javascript">
	var slideshow = new SlideShow(jQuery('#container'));
	jQuery(window).bind('resize',function(){
		slideshow.update();
	});
</script>